<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV15">
<l>kayalō numakaṇka ḷeṉṟu kaḷiṟu viṉaviniṟṟī</l>
<l>rayalō raṟiyilu mīteṉṉa vārttai kaṭalkavarnta</l>
<l>puyalō ṭulāṅkoṇṭal vaṇṇaṉ puṉavēṅ kaṭattemmoṭum</l>
<l>payalō vilīrkollai kākkiṉṟa nāḷum palapalavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Are they carps, your eyes?” you stood asking about an elephant.</l>
<l>And if those nearby were to know, what talk is this? You are not a boy</l>
<l>with us on arid Vēṅkaṭam of him the colour of clouds moving along with</l>
<l>rain seized from the ocean. Many many are the days [we] guard the clearing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
